# Bun — museothyssen theme

**Front-end runtime for the theme:** Bun + `bun.lock` in `web/themes/custom/museothyssen/`.

**Drupal / Composer / Drush** stay at the project root with `ddev composer` and `ddev drush` — do not replace with Bun.

## DDEV prerequisite

[ddev-bun](https://addons.ddev.com/addons/OpenForgeProject/ddev-bun) add-on:

```bash
ddev add-on get OpenForgeProject/ddev-bun
ddev restart
```

## Commands (from the theme)

```bash
cd web/themes/custom/museothyssen

ddev bun install              # postinstall → uebertool
ddev bun run dev              # Vite :5173 (HMR with Drupal site)
ddev bun run build            # dist/ + postbuild → museothyssen_dist
ddev bun run typecheck        # tsc
ddev bun run storybook        # :6006 (or ddev storybook from repo root)
ddev front dev                # Vite :5173 + Storybook :6006 (concurrently)
ddev bun run build-storybook
```

From repo root:

```bash
ddev bun install --cwd=web/themes/custom/museothyssen
ddev exec bash -lc 'cd web/themes/custom/museothyssen && bun run build'
ddev storybook
```

After `build` or changes to `dist/*.libraries.yml`: `ddev drush cr`.

## Quick reference

| Action | Command |
|--------|---------|
| Install deps | `ddev bun install` (in theme folder) |
| Add package | `ddev bun add <pkg>` |
| Dev dependency | `ddev bun add -d <pkg>` |
| package.json script | `ddev bun run <script>` |
| Run standalone TS | `ddev bun <file.ts>` |
| One-off npm CLI | `ddev bunx <pkg>` |

## Forbidden in the theme

```bash
npm install / npm run
pnpm / yarn
node script.js
npx
```

## Vite + DDEV

- Dev: `ddev bun run dev` — requires port **5173** in `web_extra_exposed_ports` (`.ddev/config.yaml`).
- Stop dev → `ddev bun run build` + `ddev drush cr` to serve `dist/` in local production.

## Tests

Do not use `bun test` for the theme unless Vitest or another runner is added to `package.json`. Today: `ddev bun run typecheck` — see `testing.mdc`.
